  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">HFC Phase Down Management Plan - Nigeria</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Following the outcomes of the 80th Meeting of the Executive Committee of the Multilateral Fund for the Implementation of the Montreal Protocol and subsequently Decision 80/50(e), funding was approved for Nigeria to carry out Enabling Activities for HFC phase-down to facilitate the early ratification and implementation of the Kigali Amendment that has been completed in 2018, by incorporate Customs Codes for HFCs and Quota System to facilitate monitoring of HFCs importation and Develop ODS Alternatives Data Hub.</narrative>
